Query A (direct match check — best proof)

This checks whether ER claim ids exist in procedure table.

SELECT
    COUNT(*) AS ER_VISITS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN fcp.CLAIM_ID IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ER_VISITS_WITH_PROC_MATCH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN fcp.CLAIM_ID IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ER_VISITS_WITHOUT_PROC_MATCH
FROM BI_ANALYSIS.dbo.FACT_ER_VISITS ev
LEFT JOIN BI_ANALYSIS.dbo.FACT_CLAIM_PROCEDURE fcp
    ON fcp.CLAIM_ID = ev.CLAIM_ID_ER
WHERE ev.ER_STATUS = 'TRUE ER';

